2026-07-09T05:15:45.0323605Z               "message": "Verify VMC logo hash matches retrieved BIMI SVG\n\nThe BIMI check previously reported the id-pe-logotype extension was\n\"present\" without cross-checking its embedded hash against the SVG\nserved at the l= URL, so a mismatched logo/VMC pair would pass silently.\n\nParse the RFC 3709 LogotypeExtn (subjectLogo → direct → LogotypeData →\nLogotypeImage → LogotypeDetails) using System.Formats.Asn1, extract the\nhash algorithm OID and value, and compare against the SHA-256/384/512/1\nhash of the retrieved SVG bytes. Warn on mismatch, add a detail on\nmatch, and note when the SVG was unavailable to verify.",
2026-07-09T05:15:45.0328772Z               "timestamp": "2026-07-09T04:51:54Z",
2026-07-09T05:15:45.0329433Z               "tree_id": "55ac5c674c3f7fb0c278101086b97fbe6e3c73f4",
